() Tj
T*
(Cisco Secure Workload \(CSW\) supports a defined subset of this framework. The strongest) Tj
T*
(customer story is not that CSW "certifies" compliance; it is that CSW turns workload) Tj
T*
(communication and inventory into evidence that the customer, the customer's compliance team,) Tj
T*
(and the customer's assessor can review. This report describes which framework topics CSW) Tj
T*
(supports, which it does not, what evidence artifacts CSW produces, and how often the) Tj
T*
